  characteristicName: HighQuality
  characteristicDescription: Only the best for our customers. It may be more costly,
    but it's worth the premium value.
  characteristicQuestion1: Make it appear well-made but still cut corners.
  characteristicQuestion2: Use the most expensive materials with no budget planning.
  characteristicQuestion3: Invest in good materials to have long-term brand credibility.
  characteristicPreference: I want something reliable.
